contentrichtext.text: '''GTL''' may refer to : * [[Gas to liquids]], a refinery process * [[Georgia Tech Lorraine]], a campus of the Georgia Institute of Technology in Metz, France * Global Training & Logistics, a business unit of [[Lockheed Martin Corporation]] * Group [[term life insurance]], a type of life insurance that holds no cash value * GTL, a model of tram operated by [[HTM Personenvervoer]] * ''[[GT Legends]]'', a PC racing game * [[Gunning transceiver logic]], a type of electronic logic signaling * "Gym, Tan, Laundry", an expression made popular by the TV series ''[[Jersey Shore (TV series)|Jersey Shore]]'' {{disambiguation}}
